      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in showroom-ready condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a rough day in its life. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is your lucky day. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
