    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system that functions within factory tolerances. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates, and the rod bearings have been addressed using VAC Motorsports coated shells. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, notch-free engagement, paired with a 3.62 M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains neutral under lateral load. Exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster compression or UV degradation. A meticulously maintained enthusiast example with a comprehensive service dossier.",
